sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Open profile modal
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/profile
    API->>API: Validate JWT
    API->>DB: Load UserProfile

    alt Profile exists
        DB-->>API: Existing profile
        API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + profile data
    else No profile yet
        DB-->>API: No profile
        API-->>Frontend: 204 No Content
    end

    User->>Frontend: Submit profile changes
    Frontend->>API: PATCH /api/profile
    API->>API: Validate JWT and payload

    alt No existing profile
        API->>DB: Create UserProfile
    else Existing profile
        API->>DB: Update UserProfile
    end

    DB-->>API: Profile saved
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + updated profile
    Frontend-->>User: Show success feedback
